/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Umbrella Tree\"><img alt=\"Umbrella Tree\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Umbrella_Tree.png?fab757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Lawn Decoration\">Umbrella Tree</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Floopy Tree\"><img alt=\"Floopy Tree\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Floopy_Tree.png?566b44\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Lawn Decoration\">Floopy Tree</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Funbrella Tree\"><img alt=\"Funbrella Tree\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Funbrella_Tree.png?673356\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Lawn Decoration\">Funbrella Tree</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Flowering Tree\"><img alt=\"Flowering Tree\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Flowering_Tree.png?2e4578\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Lawn Decoration\">Flowering Tree</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lawn_Decoration\" title=\"Spiral Tree\"><img alt=\"Spiral Tree\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spiral_Tree.png?99e994\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class