  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Thẻ Quy hoạch Thành phố là một danh mục chế tạo dành riêng cho Hamlet DLC. Các công thức nấu ăn trong tab này không thể được tạo nguyên mẫu, thay vào đó chúng chỉ có thể được chế tạo khi đứng gần Chìa khóa Thành phố hoặc giữ nó trong Kho đồ. Nó cũng chỉ có thể truy cập được khi người chơi ra khỏi nội thất. Các vật phẩm và Công trình được chế tạo trong tab này có thể được sử dụng để xây dựng Thành phố Lợn. Tab này cũng có thể được truy cập bằng Brain of Thought.</p>",
  "title": "City Planning Tab",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Hamlet}}\n<br>\n[[File:Icon City Planning.png|thumb|Tab Icon]]\n\n{{Quote|City engineering isn't a real science.|Wilson}}\nThe '''City Planning Tab''' is a crafting category exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC. Recipes in this tab cannot be prototyped, instead they can only be crafted while standing near the [[Key to the City]] or holding it in the [[Inventory]]. It is also only accessible when the player is out of [[:Category:Interiors|interiors]]. Items and Structures crafted in this tab can be used to build a Pig City. This tab can also be accessed with the [[Brain of Thought]].\n\n== Craftable Items and Structures ==\nThe following Items and Structures can be crafted in the City Planning Tab:\n\n<gallery columns=\"6\" position=\"center\" widths=\"64\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\nFlat Stone Turf.png|[[Flat Stone Turf]]|link=Flat Stone Turf\nStone Road Turf.png|[[Stone Road Turf]]|link=Stone Road Turf\nLamp Post.png|[[Lamp Post]]|link=Lamp Post\nTown House.png|[[Town House]]|link=Town House\nThe Sterling Trough Deli.png|[[The Sterling Trough Deli]]|link=The Sterling Trough Deli\nPigg and Pigglet's General Store.png|[[Pigg and Pigglet's General Store]]|link=Pigg and Pigglet's General Store\nCurly Tails Mud Spa.png|[[Curly Tails Mud Spa]]|link=Curly Tails Mud Spa\nSwinesbury Fine Grocer's.png|[[Swinesbury Fine Grocer's]]|link=Swinesbury Fine Grocer's\nMiss Sow's Floral Arrangements.png|[[Miss Sow's Floral Arrangements]]|link=Miss Sow's Floral Arrangements\n'The Sty' Oddities Emporium.png|[['The Sty' Oddities Emporium]]|link='The Sty' Oddities Emporium\nThe Flying Pig Arcane Shop.png|[[The Flying Pig Arcane Shop]]|link=The Flying Pig Arcane Shop\nThe Boar's Tusk Weapon Shop.png|[[The Boar's Tusk Weapon Shop]]|link=The Boar's Tusk Weapon Shop\nThe Sow's Ear Hat Shop.png|[[The Sow's Ear Hat Shop]]|link=The Sow's Ear Hat Shop\nSwinesbury Mineral Exchange.png|[[Swinesbury Mineral Exchange]]|link=Swinesbury Mineral Exchange\nMy City Hall.png|[[My City Hall]]|link=My City Hall\nWatch Tower.png|[[Watch Tower]]|link=Watch Tower\nSecurity Contract.png|[[Security Contract]]|link=Security Contract\nThe Tinkerer's Tower.png|[[The Tinkerer's Tower]]|link=The Tinkerer's Tower\nSlanty Shanty.png|[[Slanty Shanty]]|link=Slanty Shanty\nBlock Hedge.png|[[Hedge|Block Hedge]]|link=Hedge\nCone Hedge.png|[[Hedge|Cone Hedge]]|link=Hedge\nLayered Hedge.png|[[Hedge|Layered Hedge]]|link=Hedge\nLayer Tree.png|[[Lawn Decoration|Layer Tree]]|link=Lawn Decoration\nIrregular Tree.png|[[Lawn Decoration|Irregular Tree]]|link=Lawn Decoration\nUmbrella Tree.png|[[Lawn Decoration|Umbrella Tree]]|link=Lawn Decoration\nFloopy Tree.png|[[Lawn Decoration|Floopy Tree]]|link=Lawn Decoration\nFunbrella Tree.png|[[Lawn Decoration|Funbrella Tree]]|link=Lawn Decoration\nFlowering Tree.png|[[Lawn Decoration|Flowering Tree]]|link=Lawn Decoration\nSpiral Tree.png|[[Lawn Decoration|Spiral Tree]]|link=Lawn Decoration\n</gallery>\n\n{{Tabs}}\n\n[[vi:Thẻ Quy Hoạch]]\n[[ko:도시 계획 탭]]"
